                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt; LL_IOC_FSSETXATTR ioctl could be used to handle inode flags&lt;br/&gt;
 setting, currently it is mainly used to hanlde project ID changing.&lt;/p&gt;

